  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Global education on-line</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">Glob&#xE1;lne vzdel&#xE1;vanie on-line</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">&lt;p&gt;Projekt prin&#xE1;&#x161;a mo&#x17E;nos&#x165; vytvori&#x165; n&#xE1;mety a aktivity GV k predmetom bilol&#xF3;gia a dejepis pre druh&#xFD; stupe&#x148; z&#xE1;kladn&#xFD;ch &#x161;k&#xF4;l. Z&#xE1;rove&#x148; umo&#x17E;n&#xED; vytvorenie port&#xE1;lu, ktor&#xFD; pon&#xFA;kne pr&#xED;stup k relevantn&#xFD;m materi&#xE1;lom u&#x10D;ite&#x13E;omk r&#xF4;znym predmetom a z r&#xF4;znych typov &#x161;k&#xF4;l.&lt;/p&gt;</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&lt;p&gt;The project&#xB4;s aim is&#xA0;to create ideas and activities of global education and implement them into biology and history subjects&#xA0; at primary schools. It also&#xA0;creates a web based&#xA0;resource platform that facilitates access to relevant teaching materials for different school subjects and&#xA0;for different types of schools.&lt;/p&gt;</narrative>
  </description>
